periment on the neutrino mass hierarchy improves\nsignificantly by splitting the total beam time into neutrino and anti-neutrino\nruns, because the matter effect term contributes to the oscillation amplitudes\nwith the opposite sign.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Jul 2011 01:50:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Sep 2011 08:44:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
